Class Plant

java.lang.Object
pkgMain.Plant
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Plant
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
The plant class represents a plant that can support different leps and grow in different conditions.

rbila
